# ===== 白名单：默认忽略所有顶层内容，只发布 Quarto 书 =====
/*

# 仅保留以下内容
!/Causal Inference/
!/Causal Inference-EN/
!/docs/
!/data/
!/README.md
!/LICENSE
!/.gitignore

# ===== 源项目里的构建产物 / 临时文件，无需进仓库 =====
Causal Inference/.quarto/
Causal Inference/_book/
Causal Inference/.Rproj.user/
Causal Inference-EN/.quarto/
Causal Inference-EN/_book/
Causal Inference-EN/.Rproj.user/
**/.DS_Store

# Quarto 图片目录中的转换临时文件/源矢量图（不进仓库）
Causal Inference/chapters/images/tmp*.png
Causal Inference/chapters/images/*.pdf
Causal Inference/chapters/images/*.emf
